# Styling Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Prefer Tailwind over inline styles
- Use `@tailwindcss/forms` for form styling

## Custom Colors
- `primary`: #f59e0b
- `secondary`: #9ca3af
- `nonActive`: #667085
- Custom blue shades: `blue-400` (#2589FE), `blue-500` (#0070F3), `blue-600` (#2F6FEB)
- `orangeLight`: #fbbf24

## Conditional Classes
- Use `clsx` for conditional classes

## Icons
- Use Lucide React icons (`lucide-react`)
